OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens have said the
OL,7,FSNP's current childcare pledges are
OL,8,F"lacking in detail" as they urge the
OL,9,Fparty to match their universal free
OL,10,Fchildcare pledge.
OL,12,FIn a letter sent to First Minister
OL,13,FJohn Swinney, Scottish Greens co-
OL,14,Fleader Gillian Mackay said the two
OL,15,Fparties have previously "worked
OL,16,Ftogether effectively".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]wD@YOUxD@UO]
