CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777633372
OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,FHowever, she said that the SNP
OL,7,Fchildcare plans were "lacking detail
OL,8,Fso far, with no confirmation of how
OL,9,Fmany hours will be funded, who will be
OL,10,Feligible, or how they will access
OL,11,Fthem".
OL,13,FThe Scottish Greens are offering all
OL,14,Ffamilies in Scotland 1,140 hours of
OL,15,Ffunded childcare from the week after a
OL,16,Fchild turns two, which they have
OL,17,Fpledged would be delivered as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible after the election.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
