FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777633372
OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,FIn the SNP's manifesto, all children
OL,7,Ffrom nine months to the end of primary
OL,8,Fschool would be entitled to childcare.
OL,10,FThe system will be tapered based on
OL,11,Ffamily income, with the lowest-income
OL,12,Fhouseholds receiving the care for free.
OL,14,FMs Mackay said: "We all agree that
OL,15,FScotland's childcare system is not
OL,16,Fgood enough. It is expensive,
OL,17,Finflexible and forces too many parents
OL,18,Fto make really difficult choices about
OL,19,Fwhen to go back to work.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777633372
OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,F"This is an area where all parties
OL,7,Fshould be able to work together.
OL,9,F"That's why we are urging John Swinney
OL,10,Fto match our ambition and work with us
OL,11,Fto deliver the biggest rollout of free
OL,12,Fchildcare for a generation, ensuring
OL,13,Fthat no child is left behind and that
OL,14,Fno family falls through the cracks of
OL,15,Fa means-tested system.
OL,17,F"When we invest in childcare we are
OL,18,Finvesting in parents and children and
OL,19,Fin building a society where families
OL,20,Fcan flourish.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
