OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777633372
OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,F"Scotland's parents and their children
OL,7,Fdeserve a better deal. And every vote
OL,8,Ffor the Scottish Greens on May 7th is
OL,9,Fa vote to deliver it."
OL,11,FThe Scottish Greens have also pledged
OL,12,Fto invest in staffing and nursery
OL,13,Ffacilities with the aim to ensure that
OL,14,Fby the end of the parliamentary
OL,15,Fsession all families with children
OL,16,Faged six months to two years can also
OL,17,Faccess 570 hours of fully funded
OL,18,Fchildcare.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]
