OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,FJenny Gilruth, SNP candidate for Mid
OL,7,FFife and Glenrothes, said: "The SNP
OL,8,Fhas transformed childcare in Scotland
OL,9,F` providing 1,140 hours of free, high-
OL,10,Fquality early learning and childcare,
OL,11,Fworth around #6,000 to families every
OL,12,Fyear. But we have heard from families
OL,13,Facross Scotland who need more support.
OL,15,F"A re-elected SNP government will
OL,16,Fextend childcare for every child in
OL,17,Four country from nine months old to
OL,18,Fthe end of primary school ` available
OL,19,F52 weeks per year.
OL,26,@oD@\OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
