CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777633372
OL,3,CScottish Greens urge SNP to match
OL,4,Cuniversal free childcare pledge
OL,6,F"We will deliver a system that fits
OL,7,Faround families ` rather than
OL,8,Fexpecting families to fit around the
OL,9,Fsystem. That will mean families
OL,10,Fbenefit from between #1,400 up to over
OL,11,F#11,000 dependent on need.
OL,13,F"Every single family in Scotland will
OL,14,Fget help.
OL,16,F"That is what you get by voting SNP on
OL,17,FMay 7 ` a first minister and an SNP
OL,18,FGovernment always on Scotland's side."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOUzD@fO]
